text: Bugaba is a corregimiento in Bugaba District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 3,718 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,989; its population as of 2000 was 2,817. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
